2.00	Close_Your_Eyes_(hardcore_band)	Close Your Eyes (band)	Close Your Eyes is a melodic hardcore band from Abilene, Texas. They are signed to Victory Records and have released their debut album in 2010, We Will Overcome, and a second album Empty Hands and Heavy Hearts in October 2011. The music video for their first music single, "Song for the Broken", has become a viral internet video and has gathered over 2 million views in a short time. All members of Close Your Eyes are openly Christian and their beliefs are often the subject matter of their songs.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6a/Close_You_Eyes_performing_live.jpg/220px-Close_You_Eyes_performing_live.jpg
